criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  older than 18 years;

          -  less than 90 years;

          -  glomerular filtration rate between 25 and 70 ml / min;

          -  proteinuria in the urine 24 hours more than 300 mg or protein / creatinina in isolated
             urine greater than 0.3g / g or microalbuminuria (albumin / creatinine ratio) between
             30-300 mg / g.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnants;

          -  Neoplasia carrier;

          -  Renal transplant patients;

          -  Patients who refuse to participate in the study.

          -  Glomerulopathy on Immunosuppression
